1. *Poludela* sam od čekanja. (I went crazy from waiting.)
2. Ona je *poludela* kad je videla svoj pokvareni automobil. (She went crazy when she saw her broken car.)
3. *Poludeo* je kad je video račun za struju. (He went crazy when he saw the electricity bill.)
4. Sve su životinje u zoološkom vrtu *poludele* od buke vatrogasaca. (All the animals in the zoo went crazy from the noise of the firefighters.)
5. *Poludela* je od radosti kad je saznala da je dobila posao. (She went crazy with joy when she found out she got the job.)
6. Nisam znao da možeš tako *poludeti* zbog neke knjige. (I didn't know you could go crazy over a book like that.)
7. *Poludeo* je kad je video da mu je neko ukrao bicikl. (He went crazy when he saw that someone had stolen his bike.)
8. Njegova ljubomora ga je *poludela*. (His jealousy drove him crazy.)
9. *Poludeti* ću od dosade ako ostanem ovde još dugo. (I'll go crazy from boredom if I stay here any longer.)
10. Svi su *poludeli* kad su videli da se slavni glumac pojavio u njihovom gradu. (Everyone went crazy when they saw the famous actor in their town.)